## Technical Architecture

```
User uploads PDF / YouTube URL
          ↓
   Text Extraction
   PDF → pdfplumber     YouTube → yt_dlp (audio) → Whisper (transcript)
          ↓
   Text Cleaning
   Remove headers, footers, page numbers, excessive whitespace
          ↓
   Dynamic Chunking
   RecursiveCharacterTextSplitter (size scales with doc size)
          ↓
   Embedding
   all-MiniLM-L6-v2 (SentenceTransformers / HuggingFace)
   384-dimensional vectors
          ↓
   Vector Storage
   ChromaDB (local) → Qdrant Cloud (deployment)
   cosine similarity index (HNSW)

─────────────────────────────────────

User asks a question
          ↓
   Question Embedding
   Same model → 384-dim vector
          ↓
   Hybrid Retrieval
   ChromaDB/Qdrant → top N*3 semantic results
   BM25 scoring on same candidates
   Combined score: 0.7×semantic + 0.3×BM25
   Re-ranked → top N chunks
          ↓
   Context Assembly
   Chunks formatted with source hints [📄 PDF] / [📺 VIDEO]
   Page numbers and timestamps included
          ↓
   Groq LLaMA (llama-3.3-70b-versatile)
   System prompt enforces structured answer format
   Only uses provided context (no hallucination)
          ↓
   Structured Answer with citations → User
```

