## Retrieval Pipeline Detail

**Why Hybrid (BM25 + Semantic)?**

| Retrieval Type | Strength | Weakness |
|---|---|---|
| Semantic only | Finds meaning, synonyms, related concepts | Misses exact terms (names, codes, titles) |
| BM25 only | Exact keyword matching | Doesn't understand meaning |
| Hybrid (this project) | Best of both worlds | Slightly more compute |

Example: Searching "Kahneman System 2 slow thinking"
- Semantic finds pages about deliberate, effortful cognition even if those words aren't used
- BM25 ensures pages that literally say "System 2" rank high
- Combined → best results

