## Current Local Stack

| Component | Technology | Why |
|---|---|---|
| API Server | FastAPI + Uvicorn | Fast, async, modern Python |
| PDF Extraction | pdfplumber | Better than PyPDF2 for layout-heavy books |
| Text Splitting | LangChain RecursiveCharacterTextSplitter | Respects sentence/paragraph boundaries |
| Embedding Model | all-MiniLM-L6-v2 (SentenceTransformers) | 80MB, fast on CPU, good quality |
| Vector Database | ChromaDB (local persistent) | Zero setup, file-based |
| YouTube Download | yt_dlp | Works on any public YouTube video |
| Transcription | faster-whisper (base model) | No API needed, runs on CPU |
| LLM | Groq → llama-3.3-70b-versatile | Free tier, fast inference |
| Frontend | HTML + CSS + Vanilla JS | Zero dependencies, single file |

