## Planned Cloud Deployment Stack (Fully Free)

| Component | Technology | Free Tier |
|---|---|---|
| Vector Database | Qdrant Cloud (Mumbai/ap-south-1) | 1GB RAM, 4GB disk — forever |
| Embedding | fastembed (replaces sentence-transformers) | No torch — runs in 200MB RAM |
| Whisper | **Groq Whisper API** (whisper-large-v3) | Free tier — fast cloud transcription |
| LLM | Groq → llama-3.3-70b-versatile | 6000 req/day, 500k tokens/day |
| Backend Hosting | Render.com free tier | 750 hours/month |
| Frontend | Served by FastAPI (same server) | Included |
| **Total Cost** | | **$0/month** |

### Groq Whisper API — Free Tier Details
- Model: whisper-large-v3 (better than local base model)
- Free tier: generous audio minutes per day
- Replaces local faster-whisper entirely
- No ffmpeg needed on server
- Much faster than local CPU transcription

### Why Qdrant over ChromaDB for deployment
- ChromaDB is file-based — no persistent disk on free hosting
- Qdrant Cloud gives a real database endpoint with API key
- Mumbai region = low latency for South India users
- Free forever (just ping weekly to avoid inactivity suspension)

