## Current Limitations

- **Local only** — no multi-user support yet
- **CPU bound** — embedding and Whisper transcription slow without GPU
- **No streaming** — answers appear all at once, not word by word
- **No OCR** — scanned PDFs (image-based) won't extract text
- **English primary** — Whisper supports others but prompts are English-only
- **Qdrant free inactivity** — cluster suspended after 1 week without use (ping to keep alive)

